headline: WTW to Announce First Quarter Earnings on April 24, 2025
summary: LONDON, April 03, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- WTW (NASDAQ: WTW), a leading global advisory, broking and solutions company, will announce its financial results for the first quarter on Thursday, April 24, 2025 before the market opens. The company will host a conference call to discuss its financial results at 9:00 a.m. Eastern Time on Thursday, April 24, 2025.
